      <section eId="sec_CHC-1556">
        <num>CHC 1556</num>
        <heading>1556. Â Declaration for the benefit of a terminally ill child</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1556__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The parent or guardian has actual notice of contrary indications by the affected child.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1556__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The parent or guardian has actual notice of opposition to the decision by the other parent or by the child's guardian.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=73014</p>
